## How to build the docker image

1. Copy ballerina-tools-0.964.0.zip
2. Use the following command to build the docker image

docker build -t pubudu/helloworld:v1 .

## How to run the docker image

docker run -d pubudu/helloworld:v1

## Access the service

http://172.17.0.2:9090/helloWorld/sayHello
http://172.17.0.2:9090/helloWorld/delayHello


## View logs

docker logs <Container_ID>

## Bash into a running container

docker exec -it <Container_id> bash